result.name: Social Room

reviews.text: Can’t spoil it. Go and find out what it’s about.

Right now it has to be (overall) the best club for real Techno and House music  in Hong Kong. Sound system recently improved so it’s quite good. Air con works well so it’s not hot or stuffy, deco is right and it has a pretty decent and friendly bar. Only two toilets though so be prepared to queue a little at times.

Best underground-style club in Hong Kong with the highest tier techno (and sometimes breaks or idm) and decent prices on drinks. Good atmosphere and good people. Spent New Years 2019 here and the music was so good that we didn't even do the countdown.
It's ok..meh on the social
Nice place, nice music, nice stff
